  "text": "Experimental studies on C3-C12 systems, with both chain ends capped by tert-butyl groups have been reported [CITATION_1] . In the current study, this family of homology compounds was selected and modeled for direct verification of the accuracy of our theoretical vibrational frequencies with respect to Scheme 1 Ethylene and model all-trans (top) and all-cis (bottom) polyenes containing 2-14 conjugated C = C units reported experimental harmonic frequencies for these endsubstituted polyenes [CITATION_2] , and only C = C and C-C bond lengths and the corresponding stretch frequencies were analyzed.",
